- Standardize the loading state UI across all dashboard tabs and refactor redundant map component logic to improve performance and code quality.

## Constraints & Preferences
- Refactor the loading animation to be consistent across all tabs.
- Identify and refactor common code patterns.
- Ensure the loading indicator is visibly animating.

## Progress
