## Key Decisions
- Created a standalone `LoadingSpinner` component to replace disparate `<p>Loading...</p>` strings and unify visual feedback.
- Opted to keep inline `<p>` tags for embedded map loading states to prevent the `60vh` min-height of the `LoadingSpinner` from breaking card layouts.

## Next Steps
