- `frontend/src/styles/layout.css`: Contains the spinner animation and container styles.
- `frontend/src/pages/EconomicDashboard.jsx`: Primary dashboard page utilizing the new spinner.
- `frontend/src/components/maps/BuildingsMap.jsx`: Map component refactored for code cleanup.
- `frontend/src/hooks/useMapData.js`: Centralized hook for map data that should be used by all map views.

